From: 
To: 
Cc: 
Subject: US v. Maxwell, 20 Cr. 330 (AJN) - Joint Proposed Juror Questionnaire and Voir Dire 
Date: Mon, 11 Oct 2021 23:53:59 +0000 
Attachments: 2021.10.11 Letter re Jury Questionnaire and Voir Dire [to Court].pdf; _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ 
Joint_Proposed_Voir_Dire Jto_Court].pdf; 
Joint Maxwell _ Jury _Questionnaire Jto Court].pdf 
Good evening, 
Attached please find the parties' joint proposed juror questionnaire and voir dire. Per the attached letter, the parties 
respectfully request that the Court accept the joint proposed juror questionnaire and voir dire under seal. 
In addition, the Government has produced Jencks Act material and exhibits to the defense today. If the Court would like a 
copy, we would be happy to provide it. 
Respectfully submitted, 
Assistant United States Attorney 
United States Attorney's Office 
Southern District of New York 
Ne 07 
Tel 
EFTA00013430
